345
00:14:25,072 --> 00:14:28,452
So, um, how are you
handling taking a break?

346
00:14:28,534 --> 00:14:31,874
Great. Turns out Adele was right.

347
00:14:31,954 --> 00:14:33,714
Ain't nothing better for songwriting

348
00:14:33,789 --> 00:14:36,879
